63">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21737493/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Management+of+cardiac+sarcoidosis+in+the+United+States%3A+a+Delphi+study&amp;author=NY+Hamzeh&amp;author=FS+Wamboldt&amp;author=HD+Weinberger&amp;publication_year=2012&amp;journal=Chest&amp;pages=154-162&amp;doi=10.1378%2Fchest.11-0263&amp;pmid=21737493">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">31.</div><div id="r31" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Kato Y, Morimoto S, Uemura A, Hiramitsu S, Ito T, Hishida H. Efficacy of corticosteroids in sarcoidosis presenting with atrioventricular block. <em>Sarcoidosis Vasc Diffuse Lung Dis</em> 2003;20(2):133–137.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12870723/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Efficacy+of+corticosteroids+in+sarcoidosis+presenting+with+atrioventricular+block&amp;author=Y+Kato&amp;author=S+Morimoto&amp;author=A+Uemura&amp;author=S+Hiramitsu&amp;author=T+Ito&amp;author=H+Hishida&amp;publication_year=2003&amp;journal=Sarcoidosis+Vasc+Diffuse+Lung+Dis&amp;pages=133-137&amp;pmid=12870723">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">32.</div><div id="r32" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Yodogawa K, Seino Y, Shiomura R, et al. Recovery of atrioventricular block following steroid therapy in patients with cardiac sarcoidosis. <em>J Cardiol</em> 2013;62(5):320–325.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jjcc.2013.07.007">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.go